    "Name": "Miranda RR-S7M",
    "Details": "The Miranda RR-S7M is the first BattleMech produced by Firefly Foundry specifically for Firefly Stables' Solaris VII light-class tournament circuit. A 200-rated XXL engine pushes the 25-ton frame to nearly 130 kph while six jump jets add positional flexibility in the arena. Primary firepower comes from a Light PPC fitted with an experimental PPC Capacitor. Twin ER Small Lasers, an ER Medium Laser and a single-use Rocket Launcher 20 fill out the arsenal.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
